"tag-idolatry-shirk","tag-images","tag-mosques-masjid","tag-people-of-the-book-ahl-kitab","tag-warning-al-nudhr","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9Bu","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":7649,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/prophet-removes-graven-images\/","url_meta":{"origin":36920,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: The Prophet removes graven images from home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the house while there was a curtain with pictures on it. The color of his face changed, then he grabbed the curtain and tore it into pieces. The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, among the most severely punished on the Day\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11050,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/khalq-graven-images-idolatry\/","url_meta":{"origin":36920,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Folly of trying to rival Allah&#8217;s creation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: Who is more unjust than one who considers his creation as My creation? Let him create the smallest ant, or let him create a grain of wheat or barely.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7559,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link"